org.dlw.ai.blackboard.rule
Class Rule

java.lang.Object
  org.dlw.ai.blackboard.domain.BaseObject
      org.dlw.ai.blackboard.rule.Rule
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Rule
extends BaseObject

This class defines a rule for the blackboard framework. Rules are kept in a collection within the knowledge source for the default implementation and apply specifically to statements given by the subject KnowledgeSource.

Rule - "(def.) a law or principle that operates within a particular sphere of knowledge, describing or prescribing what is possible or allowable : the rules of grammar."

Version:
1.0.0-RC
Author:
David L. Whitehurst
